18#include <stddef.h>
19#include <stringlist.h>
20
21int
22main(void)
23{
24 StringList *sl;
25 char teststr[] = "test";
26
27 if ((sl = sl_init()) == NULL)
28 return 1;
29 if (sl_add(sl, teststr))
30 return 2;
31 if (sl->sl_cur != 1)
32 return 3;
33 if (sl->sl_str[0] != teststr)
34 return 4;
35
36 sl_free(sl, 0);
37 return 0;
38}
